tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review:
Highly recommended!!! Our journey with mam started from pregnancy check ups..she asked only for important blood tests *** ****** ******* *** *********** *********** ** ***** *** She is approachable and quickly responds in case of important queries. At 9th month of scan I come to know that cord around baby but she approached with positive hope and timely decision.

Dear Florence Mam,
You just glow with your presence for us and I'm sure your nature in taking care of us might have not let you know the kind of impact you made on us with this journey to make it more smooth and memorable. We're overflowing with gratitude as we reflect on the incredible journey of bringing my daughter into the world, and it's impossible to express just how thankful I am for your exceptional care.

Your expertise transformed what could have been a daunting experience into a beautiful and natural miracle. Your unwavering support was our anchor, and your calm demeanor provided a sense of reassurance that made all the difference.

We used to talk about you in most of our conversations during our pregnancy as that's the kind of conversation and connect we have had with you.

Thank you, from the depths of my heart, for playing such a vital role in the arrival of our daughter.

tags: Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Doctor friendliness,
review:
My sister referenced Dr.Florence to me as she was consulting for a PCOD problem. I had the same problem, so I was getting treatment from Cherub fertility clinic since last year. I really love the way she treats patient, Dr. Florence was very kind and friendly. The best thing is that we can get in touch with her for any clarifications at any time through Whatsapp. She is easily approachable and understand the patient very well.

Initially I had treated with PCOD and then infertility problems. I am much satisfied with the treatment she has given for pregnancy.  we can book appointment on your comfortable time as the Doctor is available in the morning and evening. I would really recommend people who is trying for Pregnancy or if any infertility problems.

tags: None
review:
Dr Florence is One of the best Gynecologist.
Have visited a dozen of other gynecologists in Chennai but was never satisfied, everyone suggested with immediate Fertility Treatment. 
On the other hand, Dr Florence was able to identify my problem during the initial visits and she was much patient and encouraging with normal process instead of Treatments on the first go. Now we are much satisfied and having SUCCESSFUL progress.
One very good aspect is individual attention and support for a patient is met and Dr immediately responds to Phone Calls and messages.
She is one of the down-to-earth doctor providing very good diagnosis and treatment.
 We would strongly recommend this Doctor.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: Me and my husband have some issues related conceiving. We had visited other doctor before in a reputed hospital but the doctor was rude didn't explain and didn't even hear our issues or concerns and want us to do as said,  remain silent and pay bills. I was so exhausted there. One of my friend's relative then recommended Dr. Florence for fertility treatment. We both were in a dillema whether to reach her or not due to last doctor experience. But from the first day Dr. Florence is very friendly, calm and understanding. Not only she explains everything politely, she always ready to hear our concerns and solve them. Me and husband both are very impressed by her and now I am getting treated by her.

tags: None
review: Dr.Florece is more friendly and easily approachable. We can meet or call for any health issue at any time. She is challenging person in making the mother in Normal delivery at any point of situation. For our both the babies she made as normal delivery and she stayed in hospital for 5 hrs in hospital to take care of my wife and made made my wife to give normal delivery. Actually othet Dr. Won't do that, if its getting late they used to prefer C-Section to cut the timing. But Dr. Florence is not like that. So we would preferred this Dr. Thank you Dr. Thanks once again.we are getting the clinical help from this Dr from 2013 to till date. Thanks from - Mani Sankareswari Panneer Selvam. Koushik avenue, Rajakilpakkam..
